title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Russo/Grimm/Birk/Keenum
description: Wild coach Bruce Boudreau kicks off the show, followed by Russo in studio. Gophers vox Mike Grimm joins midway through, Matt Birk in studio final hour, and locker room audio from Vikes QB Case Keenum!
